Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:31.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Damn, there's just too many of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:41.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Are you having difficulties, Edward Elric?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:47.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,How can one struggle against a lumbering enemy whose only strength is in its numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:50.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Behold, these deformations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:53.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Behold! The marriage of alchemy and physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Passed down the Armstrong line for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:01:08.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Witness the art of alchemy combined with physical strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:11.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,That wasn't too much, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:15.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,It's so hard holding yourself back in battle when you're fighting brainless drones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:23.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:28.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,My sincerest apologies, Lieutenant. We did mean to arrive a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:31.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Geez, don't you guys know how to come onto a scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Without making a scene, you're so attention-starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:37.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Right. You knew I'd have to show my face sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,So how have things been going, Fullmetal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:42.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Looks like this was a close call. Guess that means you owe me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:48.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I don't owe you anything. These golems couldn't get an inch on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,And now, you owe me two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:55.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,If you're my backup, then back me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:02:00.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,That's funny. But I'm not here for backup, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:05.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,You've fought bravely enough. Now you can leave it in the hands of the state.
